{"tid":1059371,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"c朗拿度激起美斯鬥志， 今晚巴塞贏鳩硬","createTime":"2019-03-13T05:35:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T05:55:41.000Z","uid":43785,"like":38,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"de1b338304b433897383635506ce569abea83f06","tid":1059371,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T05:35:54.000Z","msg":"既生瑜，何生亮<br />\nc朗拿度自從離開咗皇家馬德里之後與美斯再難以碰頭交鋒。<br />\n美斯如果想再次挑戰c朗拿度證明自己， 今晚巴塞羅拿一定會出盡渾身解數去戰勝里昂。<br />\n<br />\n更何況史浩克04 及里昂， 被譽為是似歐聯最弱的兩隊16強。<br />\n就咁睇巴塞羅拿嘅人腳 ，前中後場冇一個會輸畀里昂<br />\n相信今晚巴塞一定會給他顏色。 美斯亦會出盡渾身解數去證明自己是球王者一點。<br />\n<br />\n所以今晚巴塞羅那一定贏， 有美斯絕對不會輸。 最大宿敵皇馬，馬體會， 羅馬以被踢走。<br />\n今年歐聯巴塞羅拿冠軍在望。<br />\n<br />\n祖雲達斯與c朗拿度，我哋8強見。"},{"pid":"e8a572461aaf0a6eef7f69196ea1ec5a019c70f7","tid":1059371,"uid":45498,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T05:38:32.000Z","msg":"洗撚你講 巴菜贏<span style=\"color: orange;\">鳩硬</span>"},{"pid":"a25e667196c94a657707cdb6648453625d588072","tid":1059371,"uid":149008,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T05:40:26.000Z","msg":"無褲著 無親戚，既生瑜 何生亮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dd1d4403465ab46c0bc9a85ec676536145bd639","tid":1059371,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T05:45:02.000Z","msg":"有限錢嘅兄弟 想上樓嘅兄弟 想買車嘅兄弟<br />\n各位聽住啦<br />\n今晚買巴塞羅拿晉級100%收錢<br />\n完全係冇得輸。<br />\n 夠膽嘅就一齊跟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有錢齊齊搵巴塞晉級齊齊慶祝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a8636e41bb077b5f0b9f191babfd66b964110d2","tid":1059371,"uid":45498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"qu